mindmap
  root((MLOps))
    Five Core Domains
      Data versioning - lineage - auditability
      Experiment tracking - logging - reproducibility
      CI-CD for model validation - deployment automation
      Monitoring - drift detection - retraining - rollback
      Governance - compliance - explainability
    Stack Components
      Feature stores for consistency - reuse across teams
      Model registry as production source of truth
      Observability tools for prediction - data health
      Security - access controls - audit logging
    CAIO Strategy
      Assess maturity before selecting tools
      Embed governance into pipelines from day one
      Design for reuse - build compounding capital
      Centralized platform - decentralized product teams
    Anti-Patterns
      Infrastructure before workflow definition
      Over-tooling without system integration
      MLOps as project - not organizational transformation
      Rewarding heroics over reliable - boring infrastructure